abstract: If either Elizabeth Warren or Amy Klobuchar is going to win the 2020 Democratic U.S. presidential nomination, they will have to take down Pete Buttigieg to do it.
snippet: If either Elizabeth Warren or Amy Klobuchar is going to win the 2020 Democratic U.S. presidential nomination, they will have to take down Pete Buttigieg to do it.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — If either Elizabeth Warren or Amy Klobuchar is going to win the 2020 Democratic U.S. presidential nomination, they will have to take down Pete Buttigieg to do it.
headline_main: Blitzing Buttigieg: Democratic U.S. Presidential Rivals Train Debate Attacks on Young Mayor
headline_print_headline: Blitzing Buttigieg: Democratic U.S. Presidential Rivals Train Debate Attacks on Young Mayor

abstract: The U.S. military plans to stockpile rare earth magnets used in Javelin missiles and F-35 fighter jets, according to a government document seen by Reuters, a step that critics say does little to help create a domestic industry to build specialized magnets now made almost exclusively in Asia.
snippet: The U.S. military plans to stockpile rare earth magnets used in Javelin missiles and F-35 fighter jets, according to a government document seen by Reuters, a step that critics say does little to help create a domestic industry to build specialized...
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - The U.S. military plans to stockpile rare earth magnets used in Javelin missiles and F-35 fighter jets, according to a government document seen by Reuters, a step that critics say does little to help create a domestic industry to build specialized magnets now made almost exclusively in Asia.
headline_main: Exclusive: Pentagon to Stockpile Rare Earth Magnets for Missiles, Fighter Jets
headline_print_headline: Exclusive: Pentagon to Stockpile Rare Earth Magnets for Missiles, Fighter Jets

abstract: Catastrophic conditions fuelled massive bushfires across Australia's New South Wales state on Saturday, with three blazes around Sydney burning at emergency level, while in South Australia one person was found dead in a fire zone.
snippet: Catastrophic conditions fuelled massive bushfires across Australia's New South Wales state on Saturday, with three blazes around Sydney burning at emergency level, while in South Australia one person was found dead in a fire zone.
lead_paragraph: SYDNEY — Catastrophic conditions fuelled massive bushfires across Australia's New South Wales state on Saturday, with three blazes around Sydney burning at emergency level, while in South Australia one person was found dead in a fire zone.
headline_main: Bushfires Hit Emergency Level on Sydney's Outskirts; One Dead in South Australia
headline_print_headline: Bushfires Hit Emergency Level on Sydney's Outskirts; One Dead in South Australia

abstract: Australia's second-largest lender Westpac Banking Corp on Friday appointed two people to a panel which will assess the bank's accountability in a money laundering scandal.
snippet: Australia's second-largest lender Westpac Banking Corp on Friday appointed two people to a panel which will assess the bank's accountability in a money laundering scandal.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - Australia's second-largest lender Westpac Banking Corp on Friday appointed two people to a panel which will assess the bank's accountability in a money laundering scandal.
headline_main: Australia's Westpac Names Two Members of Money Laundering Review Panel
headline_print_headline: Australia's Westpac Names Two Members of Money Laundering Review Panel

abstract: Recent hits like “Flirty Dancing” and stalwarts like “The Great British Baking Show” offer gentle escapism in a genre better known for manipulating participants for entertainment.

lead_paragraph: LONDON — Michael Chakraverty was having a panic attack on reality TV.

abstract: A court sentenced a former lawmaker from India's ruling party to life imprisonment for raping a teenager, his lawyer said on Friday, the highest ranking Indian politician to get such a significant jail term in recent years.
snippet: A court sentenced a former lawmaker from India's ruling party to life imprisonment for raping a teenager, his lawyer said on Friday, the highest ranking Indian politician to get such a significant jail term in recent years.
lead_paragraph: LUCKNOW — A court sentenced a former lawmaker from India's ruling party to life imprisonment for raping a teenager, his lawyer said on Friday, the highest ranking Indian politician to get such a significant jail term in recent years.
headline_main: Indian Court Hands Life Term to Ex-Lawmaker for Rape

abstract: With a voice known to millions of Indian moviegoers, Zubeen Garg   crooned one of his old songs with patriotic fervour, but he is  protesting against the government, not singing its praises.
snippet: With a voice known to millions of Indian moviegoers, Zubeen Garg   crooned one of his old songs with patriotic fervour, but he is  protesting against the government, not singing its praises.
lead_paragraph: GUWAHATI, India — With a voice known to millions of Indian moviegoers, Zubeen Garg crooned one of his old songs with patriotic fervour, but he is protesting against the government, not singing its praises.
headline_main: India's Protesters Cheered On by Actors, Artists and Singers

abstract: One of China's biggest animal feed producers said it had used a radio transmitter to combat crooks using drones to drop pork products contaminated with African swine fever on its pig farms, as part of a racket to profit from the health scare.

lead_paragraph: BEIJING — One of China's biggest animal feed producers said it had used a radio transmitter to combat crooks using drones to drop pork products contaminated with African swine fever on its pig farms, as part of a racket to profit from the health scare.
headline_main: Commercial Pig Farm in China Jams Drone Signal to Combat Swine Fever Crooks

abstract: China said Friday its relationship with the United States had experienced serious difficulties, but they should work in accordance with the consensus reached by the two countries' leaders to push forward a stable bilateral relationship.

abstract: The U.S. Ambassador to the United Nations made a rare compassionate public gesture toward her Iranian counterpart in the Security Council chamber on Thursday, expressing condolences over the death of an Iranian toddler.
snippet: The U.S. Ambassador to the United Nations made a rare compassionate public gesture toward her Iranian counterpart in the Security Council chamber on Thursday, expressing condolences over the death of an Iranian toddler.
lead_paragraph: UNITED NATIONS — The U.S. Ambassador to the United Nations made a rare compassionate public gesture toward her Iranian counterpart in the Security Council chamber on Thursday, expressing condolences over the death of an Iranian toddler.
headline_main: In Rare Move, U.S. and Iranian Envoys Talk After U.N. Meeting on Nuclear Deal
